    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.03720.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place" rend="right">Camden NJ</name>
                    <date when="1880-12-06" rend="right"><hi rend="underline">12th 6th 1880.</hi></date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Walt Whitman</salute>
                <salute>My Dear "Old Boy"</salute>
            </opener>
            
            <p>I was so full, Sunday, of the "ample ether, and the divine air" of your presence<ptr target="n1049"/>&#8212;and the <hi rend="underline">aurum potabile</hi> which always surrounds our <hi rend="underline">symposiums</hi>
            
                <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.03720.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
                <pb xml:id="leaf002r" facs="loc.03720.003_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            
            that I forgot to say that I expended $9.50 in pursuit of the <hi rend="underline">recalcitrant, pirate</hi>&#8212;Worthington,<ptr target="loc.03720_n1"/> in New York City.</p>
            
            <p>Please send me this amount by Bearer, &amp; oblige Your Devoted but "<hi rend="underline">impecunious</hi>" friend</p>
                       
            <closer>
                <signed rend="right"><hi rend="underline">J M Scovel</hi></signed>
            </closer>
            
            <postscript><p>PS. If you want me further, you know how to "whistle" &amp; "I <hi rend="underline">will come to you my lad</hi>.</p></postscript>
            
            <pb xml:id="leaf002v" facs="loc.03720.004_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
            
        </body>
    </text>
